ince-brexit/</link><description>自英国公投脱欧以来，右翼民粹主义者及其政党经常扰乱欧洲的政治格局。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 02:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/05/28/right-wing-populism-in-the-decade-since-brexit/</guid></item><item><title>您对北约了解多少？参加我们的测验</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/05/27/how-much-do-you-know-about-nato-take-our-quiz/</link><description>测试您的北约知识，看看您与美国成年人相比如何。平均而言，美国人正确回答了五个事实问题中的一半。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 01:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/05/27/how-much-do-you-know-about-nato-take-our-quiz/</guid></item><item><title>美国人在教堂里听到哪些政治问题？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/2026/05/27/what-political-issues-do-americans-hear-about-in-church/</link><description>大多数参加宗教仪式的美国成年人表示，他们最近从神职人员那里听到了至少一个政治或社会问题。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 01:37:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/religion/2026/05/27/what-political-issues-do-americans-hear-about-in-church/</guid></item></channel></rss>